::NACE Framework::How many career readiness competencies does the National Association of Colleges and Employers (NACE) framework identify?{
~5 competencies #Incorrect. The NACE framework is more comprehensive, identifying 8 career readiness competencies.
=8 competencies #Correct! The NACE Career Readiness framework (revised March/April 2024) identifies 8 employer-validated competencies.
